'''The Institute of Social Sciences''' studies social, political and economic issues of contemporary relevance. It provides inputs to the policy makers and [[civil society organisation]]s.

The Institute has established the Centre for Multilevel [[Federalism]] (CMF) for the study of federalism in India.

